--------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |MULTI PARTITION DELETE          |         |1        |73  |
|1 | EXCHANGE IN DISTR              |         |1        |73  |
|2 |  EXCHANGE OUT DISTR            |         |1        |73  |
|3 |   MERGE JOIN                   |         |1        |73  |
|4 |    EXCHANGE IN MERGE SORT DISTR|         |2        |37  |
|5 |     EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (PKEY)  |         |2        |36  |
|6 |      TABLE SCAN                |case2_t_2|2        |36  |
|7 |    TABLE SCAN                  |case2_t_3|2        |36  |
==============================================================

Outputs & filters: 
-------------------------------------
